the earlier studies (see BERNEY & BLANE, 1997; BLANE, 1996) was to use the	144.6999969482422	730.7797241210938	11.000007629394531	390.9619903564453	32
LG to improve the accuracy of the recalled information (BELL, 2005). BERNEY	144.6999969482422	744.8796997070312	11.0	384.61500549316406	32
and BLANE's (1997) study assessed the accuracy of older participants' recall of	144.6999969482422	759.0797119140625	11.000007629394531	388.1902618408203	32
