Some of the practical challenges (and solutions) we encountered with the LG are	144.6999969482422	150.5797119140625	11.0	394.3941192626953	186
also important to note here. Initially, the interviewer used a semi-structured	144.6999969482422	164.7796630859375	11.0	364.17701721191406	186
