participant in identifying key questions and life events categories, such as	144.6999969482422	235.47967529296875	11.0	358.3910675048828	186
relationships, school, work etc. that will be discussed in the LG interview. It might	144.6999969482422	249.6796875	11.0	394.1081085205078	186
also be useful to identify possible life-events from the literature and incorporate	144.6999969482422	263.7796630859375	11.0	384.74708557128906	186
