6. Conclusion	144.6999969482422	107.73675537109375	12.0	78.6240234375	191
This article describes the utility of the LG in qualitative inquiries. We found the LG	144.6999969482422	136.47967529296875	11.0	397.6501007080078	192
approach useful in helping explore the breadth and depth of events as we were	144.6999969482422	150.5797119140625	11.0	385.53919982910156	192
not only interested in when significant events occurred but also the participants'	144.6999969482422	164.7796630859375	11.0	386.47413635253906	193
experiences of, and changes in, these selected areas of their lives. While the LG	144.6999969482422	178.87969970703125	11.0	393.22816467285156	193
worked well in our study, it is advisable that researchers conduct a formative	144.6999969482422	193.0797119140625	11.0	372.0420684814453	194
phase to establish key questions and life event categories so as to ensure that	144.6999969482422	207.1796875	11.0	382.4481964111328	194
their research questions are appropriately addressed. The LG as a tool and	144.6999969482422	221.37969970703125	11.0	367.6421661376953	195
approach will be particularly valuable to qualitative researchers who are	144.6999969482422	235.47967529296875	11.0	348.1169891357422	195
interested in retrospectively exploring sensitive emotional events in the	144.6999969482422	249.6796875	11.0	344.0690155029297	196
